item.title: CremePieSwap
item.description: CremePieSwap, the exchange AMM/DEX service on Polygon MATIC that everyone is talking about.  With native token $CPIE, the CremePieSwap exchange allows users to transact on Polygon, allowing further adoption of the internet of blockchains and it's cost efficiency. CPS provides a full suite of savings and investment options with liquidity pools, staking, IDO's - and a fully fledged lottery system - with more to come.
